== 製作 ==
該片首次於2013年8月公布，當時克里斯·埃文斯簽訂了一份負責編、導和演<ref name=Deadline1>{{cite web|last=Fleming Jr.|first=Mike|title=小牛試刀 「美國隊長」克里斯·埃文斯編導和演《一點半的火車》（英文版）|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/08/chris-evans-to-helm-130-train-before-reprising-captain-america-in-avengers-2/|publisher=Deadline|accessdate=29 January 2014|archive-date=2013-08-06|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6IfngyrhB?url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/08/chris-evans-to-helm-130-train-before-reprising-captain-america-in-avengers-2/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而在10月同意爱丽丝·伊芙為主演者<ref name=Variety1>{{cite web|last=McNary|first=Dave|title=Alice Eve Boards Chris Evans' '1:30 Train'|url=http://variety.com/2013/film/news/alice-eve-boards-chris-evans-130-train-1200749530/|publisher=Variety|accessdate=29 January 2014}}</ref>。

而拍攝則在2013年12月開始，位於[[曼哈頓|曼哈頓]][[下东城|下东城]]，為期19天<ref name=Yahoo>{{cite web|last=Setoodeh|first=Ramin|title=瞻前顧後 克里斯·埃文斯為拍攝準備（英文版）|url=http://movies.yahoo.com/news/captain-america-chris-evans-says-ready-leave-acting-130029033.html|publisher=Yahoo|date=25 March 2014}}</ref><ref name="NY Daily News1">{{cite web|last=Maresca|first=Rachel|title=共同晚餐（英文版）|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/gossip/chris-evans-dinner-date-co-star-alice-eve-report-article-1.1553960|publisher=NY Daily News|accessdate=29 January 2014}}</ref>。

2014年7月，{{link-en|2014年度多倫多國際電影節|2014 Toronto International Film Festival|}}公布，該片選定為首映節，並同時由《一點半的火車》更名為《紐約愛未眠》<ref>{{cite web|author1=Linda Barnard|title=TIFF shows strength with first batch of 2014 premieres|url=http://www.thestar.com/entertainment/movies/2014/07/22/tiff_unveils_first_batch_of_2014_premieres.html|publisher=Toronto Star Newspapers|accessdate=23 July 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author1=Greg Gilman|title=Captain America Cozies Up With Alice Eve in First Look at Chris Evans' Directorial Debut (Photo)|url=https://movies.yahoo.com/news/captain-america-cozies-alice-eve-first-look-chris-170400083.html|publisher=Yahoo|accessdate=23 July 2014|archive-date=2020-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200126112822/https://www.yahoo.com/entertainment/news/captain-america-cozies-alice-eve-first-look-chris-170400083.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

該片則由克里斯·威士德力克為主要作曲<ref>{{cite news|title=Chris Westlake to Score Chris Evans' 'Before We Go'|url=http://filmmusicreporter.com/2014/07/25/chris-westlake-to-score-chris-evans-before-we-go/|accessdate=August 1, 2014|publisher=filmmusicreporter.com|date=July 25, 2014}}</ref>。

